data.description: Are you looking for a lower interest rates?  This loan is assumable at 3.5% to VA eligible buyers! This beautiful 4 bed, 3 and ½ bath home sits on a corner lot. The two-story custom home features 1/3rd of an acre with beautifully mature trees backing up to Spring Creek. All surrounded by a privacy fence. You will not feel like you’re living in the middle of the city! Other features of the home include: a kitchen with island cooktop/prep area, double ovens, tiled backsplash, tons of counterspace, and dedicated area that could be a coffee/wine bar. A master suite with dedicated back yard access, master bath with garden tub, dual vanities, walk-in shower, and closet. A lower-level living area with cathedral ceilings, an abundance of natural light, and an attached flex room that could be a sun room, atrium or bonus area. The laundry room is enormous, with a lot of counterspace/storage and utility sink. The dedicated office comes complete with built-in shelving. It’s all topped off with an upstairs bonus/2nd living area that has sink, dishwasher, ice maker and a microwave. Call today for your personal private tour!
